</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance between terminals 6 (CANH) and 4 (CG), and between terminals 14 (CANL) and 4 (CG) of the DLC3 each time a connector is disconnected.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C126231E13" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
